Name: objoid
Description: The OID of the specific object

Name: classoid
Description: The OID of the system catalog the object is in

Name: objsubid
Description: For a table column, this is the column number (the objoid and classoid refer to the table itself). For all other object types, this column is zero.

Name: privtype
Description: A code defining the type of initial privilege of this object; see text

Name: initprivs
Description: The initial access privileges; see Section 5.7 for details
